transcript:
Customer: Hello
Executive: Hello
Customer: Gandhi sir
Executive: Hello
Customer: Ha ji sir wo mujhe bola tha 50 list milegi non electable wo mujhe abhi tak nahi mila sir
Executive: Ha ha are sir wo dala hua hai approval ke liye aapke pass allocate ho jayegi Monday tak mein
Customer: Monday tak aapne Monday ko bola tha ki Monday tak ho jayega wo Monday chala gaya Monday aane wala hai sir
Executive: Are sir
Executive: Maine likh ke diya hai aapko abhi main abhi main aapko mail vagera sab kuch dikha deta hu usme koi dikkat nahi hai
Executive: Aisa nahi hai ki humne bol diya aur aapko milega nahi
Executive: Wo aapko mil jayega ye ye aapne abhi call kiya customer care mein recorded line pe bhi main keh raha hu
Executive: To aap itna to trust rakhiye sir
Customer: Ha ji ye aapne customer care pe ye customer care pe dala tha call kiya hai to wo concern open ho jata hai to main isko abhi close kar deta hu Monday aapko process ho jayega wo
Customer: Mujhe kal tak aapko time dena padega
Executive: Theek hai sir aapke pass ek feedback mail aayega
